data.title: Russian squad for World Juniors
data.meta_description: Russia has confirmed her team for the 11th IAAF World Junior Championships, Beijing, China, 15-20 August 2006, as follows...
data.text:
Russia has confirmed her team for the 11th IAAF World Junior Championships, Beijing, China, 15-20 August 2006, as follows -

200m and 4x100m relay – Igor Shevtzov, Ramis Abdulkalerov

400m and 4x100m relay –Ivan Shmelev

110m H – Vladimir Zhukov

400m H – Vyacheslav Sakaev

3000m Steeplechase – Igor Chernobai
